Short: Apache2 + mod_rewrite, Python + SQLObject + CheetahTemplate, intltool

Long:

Python 2.2? 2.3? 2.4?

Python modules:
 o SQLObject for database access (http://cheeseshop.python.org/pypi/SQLObject) (package python-sqlobject on Debian/Ubuntu)
   Tested only with 0.6.1
 o Any of sqlitedb, MySQLdb, postgresdb modules
 o Cheetah for HTML templating (http://www.cheetahtemplate.org/) (package python-cheetah on Debian/Ubuntu)

Programs (need to be in PATH):
 o msgfmt
 o msgmerge
 o intltool-update
 o xml2po

intltool-update requirements:
 o Perl
 o XML::Parser
 o intltool-extract
 o xgettext

xml2po requirements:
 o libxml2 + Python bindings

